Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.08,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:03.63,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.24,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:08.32,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been studyin' real seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:11.00,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody understands that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.81,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got exams this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:15.32,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Try a little harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:18.03,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Run a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:21.33,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to sing a little louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm doin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chin up, Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just barge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' wrong with gettin' all threes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer pa got all threes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:35.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:37.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer already on the track to mediocrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bein' mediocre just makes ya unique, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya don't need somethin', get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We do need you to do somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:52.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this champon to Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:01:00.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, shouldn't you reconsider this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:04.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no need for you to \Nbe cookin' for a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:07.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tell him, "Cook your own food."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:12.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:17.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize how doin' things for \NSensei gives your mother purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With a son who can care for himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:23.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and a lethargic husband who just says \N"s'good" no matter what I feed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In a life with no challenges,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:31.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,only Sensei's existence revives my \Nheart as a mother, and as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:52.69,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Barakamon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.96,Barakamon Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakamashika
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.96,Barakamon Title Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Translation:\NAnnoying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.71,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since I came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.30,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't written anything I'm satisfied with...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.47,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just spur of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.47,MX Handwritten,,0000,0000,0000,,FUN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.01,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't call it my own style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.72,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to immerse myself in writing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.89,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and to triumph over that geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:31.78,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:36.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You again? Why do you come here every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I'm yer commuter wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miwa-nee and Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! So this's the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:54.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen someone in a \Nstylish jinbei like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:57.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't been to the base in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't come in without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:01.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! The posters're all torn down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The CDs are gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, barging in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer the one who barged in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was our base!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where's our stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you pitched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff that was in here when \NI moved in is all inside in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These're important to us, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:27.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this isn't your base anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you putting up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't got no mind to leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, leave! Someone lives here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so uptight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:41.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know yer happy to be mixin' with young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stuff that's easily misunderstood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught this child all those indecent words!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.27,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,That lady's the queen of Kabuki-cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.84,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's nice out, I'll go streetwalking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.73,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,This miso soup is labial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tellin' us that won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya just memorized stuff ya \Noverheard us sayin', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, no one taught me nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You be careful too, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:17.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids her age parrot phrases like a myna bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying, the language you use is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Esu Emu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote that for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanin' it's for an S&M Club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Esu Emu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Esu Emu! Esu Emu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.19,MX Calligraphy 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Esunic (Ethnic) Restaurant\N{\fs36}Emupamuuza
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.44,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,Esunic (Ethnic) Restaurant\N{\fs36}Emupamuuza
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for a restaurant signboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you makin', Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't use my calligraphy \Ntools without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.07,MX Calligraphy 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Loser
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:55.91,MX Calligraphy 4,,0000,0000,0000,,Loser
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Write something nicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:52.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer real good, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:53.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you're aimin' to write manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about me wantin' to write manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be better'n Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:05.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's actually easy to become a calligrapher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:12.97,MX Handwritten 2,,0000,0000,0000,,LOSER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This is real calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:29.57,MX Handwritten 3,,0000,0000,0000,,LOSER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't quite get why, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't really get it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a penmanship assignment \Nin our summer homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have Sensei look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I learn from Sensei, a big \Nprize won't be just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please help us out, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll come back tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And those feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,excite your mother as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I get it already! I'm goin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.26,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Hina this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to play right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go play outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.26,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus, focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.11,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ignore them, they'll leave eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot somethin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:46.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S&M...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come back today, any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:53.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... I feel dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.46,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.06,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We're stuck dealin' with some guy \Ntoo old to be this high-maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.34,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A calligrapher's gotta be a real snobby jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.12,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I hafta make it clear we \Ncan't go on feedin' him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I know you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, jerk! Answer when someone's calli—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:33.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi! What're you doin' to Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't doin' nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take the champon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:51.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Lend me your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said take the champon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing it's wrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so great, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, why's he on the verge of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always like that this time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been writin' stuff for \Na calligraphy contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Up all night, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get like that before tests, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:30.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, between me and a guy with talent, \NI guess all-nighters don't mean the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi, what's "talent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:36.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's when a guy can do anything \Nwith just a little effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:39.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when a guy like me can't do nothin' \Nno matter how hard he tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get all threes even though ya tried hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who'd you hear that from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like workin' hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:52.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By golly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't nobody who can beat me at {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:01.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hidden in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bargin' into a room is—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:13.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it's in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:22.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,says he still can't write nothin' good \Neven after writin' all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Sensei ain't got talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,even after writin' lots, \Nhe thinks it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.68,MX Handwritten,,0000,0000,0000,,UTMOST
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:33.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Sensei's amazin', but I \Ndon't much understand "talent."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.07,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I've studied this much already. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.77,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You dyed your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.85,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm goin' with this style from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.99,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do everything half-assed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do everything half-assed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I get all threes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:58.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, on second thought, \NSensei really does have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:04.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't actually get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were fakin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to work hard \Nis the best talent of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:15.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hiroshi, you cryin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! Yer definitely cryin'! \NAnd yer a grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cicada shells!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:34.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can beat me at collectin' these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's talent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try with all your might \Nso nobody can beat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that might be talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're the Village Chief's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have you all do so much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:58.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last time we can bring you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma won't say it, but I think \Nyou've gotten to be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a burden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:14.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I plan to study seriously \Nfor my exams from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:20.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to try following your example, \Nand make a proper effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:24.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like your mom's meat and potato \Nstew, but I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you some homemade \Nmeat and potato stew for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:40.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad if that messy champon \Nwas your last meal from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:40.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to start cooking for myself tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you gonna make rice or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll make curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to play again—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am-ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:10.68,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanatsutake Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:14.68,MX Signs 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa Sei\N\NPrivate Room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:14.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heatstroke, sleep deprivation, poor appetite...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm admitting you for one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:22.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For goodness' sake, Sensei, why didn't \Nyou say you weren't feelin' well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of ended up with insomnia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:28.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, will you get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:31.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm hooked up to an IV, so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt worse'n a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:43.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fetch what you need \Nfor stayin' the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, \Nfeel free to call on Iku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This here nurse may be young, \Nbut she's a married woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go puttin' hands on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know shots hurt worse than IVs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.41,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.97,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've been pretty tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.93,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get back to writing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:20.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you still doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put down the toy car and listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:30.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You girls came all this way to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a school day, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our middle school's near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so I'm just a side trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's still nice though, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, your IV's about to run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:56.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't it just refill itself \Nonce the bag runs out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothin' that high-tech!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Use the nurse-call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nasu {\i1}(eggplant){\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't no nasu here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:08.84,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Nasu! Nasu! Nasu, nasu, nasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't call Iku-neechan soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,air will get into Sensei's arm and he'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:21.06,MX Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1360)}Handa Sei\N\NPrivate Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no nasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The button's right by his pillow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:16.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillow-talk! Pillow-talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, Sensei fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's spineless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The recent models won't let air get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was already in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:38.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, your temperature has gone up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I insert a suppository to lower it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppository?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're {\i1}you{\i0} reacting, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:44.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to engage in humiliation-play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Humiliation-play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is standard medical care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:54.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When {\i1}that{\i0} was done to \Nme back in grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:59.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got so embarrassed that I threw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to confess your trauma to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep him under observation for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:08.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, don't go gettin' him overexcited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:11.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:16.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin' down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll dirty your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:20.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to press it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:26.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens to Sensei, \NI'll press the nasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the IV's all full now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's gonna happen for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a ghost here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grampa told me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that there's a ghost in this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scarier'n a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:43.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:47.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is, I'm scared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see it just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her grampa totally made that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not listening to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do if I hear you talking about \Nscary stuff and can't sleep tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:07.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This hospital is old, so it's really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout a suppository?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you flinch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the stuff you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And my writing tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for those!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just collapsed from overwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm most relaxed when I'm working!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.78,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid? I'm worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are goin' wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.74,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time for us to be headin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I startle you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the room next to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounded mighty lively in there earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry. Did we bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:14.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's ailin' you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing that bad, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:17.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be "just a cold."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:25.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't they all worried about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:30.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids seemed mighty relieved \Nwhen they heard you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:35.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get to feelin' better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.27,MX Calligraphy 5,,0000,0000,0000,,HEARTBEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:01.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the Village Chief \Nto bring me my writing tools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fever hasn't gone down yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:08.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to write while the idea's still fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me write!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:11.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to write it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You can't, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:19.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:31.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His fever's gone up from excitement, \Nso I'll give him a suppository for sleepin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:38.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your color does look a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to the sposi-tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fill your prescriptions. \NBe sure to take them as directed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:55.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:59.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't test my love for my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:04.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to hurry back so I can write!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're raring to go, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:10.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man in the room next to mine \Nreally cheered me up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in this room... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:21.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, where's the old man who was in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the only patient here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Most folks just go to the new facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:30.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:34.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, did ya see a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:40.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:16.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought meat and potato stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do to your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:22.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:24.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:25.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:29.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do with these \Nblood-soaked onions you cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:35.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a spice! Like Tabasco! \NThat's what the red stuff is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:41.50,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, I get the feeling I understand \Nwhat you were talking about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:45.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue to bring \Nyou food from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:48.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that great, Sensei?
